text: Annie Laurie Gunter (born Annie Laurie Cain; June 23, 1919 – July 9, 2005) was an American politician who served as the Treasurer of Alabama from 1978 to 1987. She died of heart failure on July 9, 2005, in Montgomery, Alabama at age 86. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:2005 deaths Category:State treasurers of Alabama Category:Alabama Democrats
title: Annie Laurie Gunter
